OL,3,CHead of UNRWA calls on countries to
OL,4,Creconsider 'shocking' pause in funding
OL,6,FThe head of the UN relief agency in
OL,7,FGaza has called on countries that have
OL,8,Fsuspended funding to reconsider their
OL,9,F"shocking" decision.
OL,11,FPhilippe Lazzarini said the United
OL,12,FNations Relief and Works Agency
OL,13,F(UNRWA) is depended upon by more than
OL,14,Ftwo million people for their survival.
OL,16,FIt comes after Britain joined nations
OL,17,Fincluding the US, Australia, Italy and
OL,18,FCanada in temporarily pausing support
OL,19,Ffor the organisation over claims that
OL,20,Fa number of its staff were involved in
OL,21,FHamas' October 7 attack.
