OL,3,CHead of UNRWA calls on countries to
OL,4,Creconsider 'shocking' pause in funding
OL,6,FThe UNRWA has sacked several of its
OL,7,Femployees in Gaza suspected of taking
OL,8,Fpart in last year's assault by Hamas
OL,9,Fand other militants on southern Israel.
OL,11,FIn a statement on Saturday, Mr
OL,12,FLazzarini said: "It is shocking to see
OL,13,Fa suspension of funds to the agency in
OL,14,Freaction to allegations against a
OL,15,Fsmall group of staff, especially given
OL,16,Fthe immediate action that UNRWA took
OL,17,Fby terminating their contracts and
OL,18,Fasking for a transparent independent
OL,19,Finvestigation.
