OL,3,CHead of UNRWA calls on countries to
OL,4,Creconsider 'shocking' pause in funding
OL,6,F"The United Nations Office of Internal
OL,7,FOversight Services (OIOS), the highest
OL,8,Finvestigative authority in the UN
OL,9,Fsystem, has already been seized of
OL,10,Fthis very serious matter."
OL,12,FHe added: "It would be immensely
OL,13,Firresponsible to sanction an Agency
OL,14,Fand an entire community it serves
OL,15,Fbecause of allegations of criminal
OL,16,Facts against some individuals,
OL,17,Fespecially at a time of war,
OL,18,Fdisplacement and political crises in
OL,19,Fthe region."
