OL,3,CHead of UNRWA calls on countries to
OL,4,Creconsider 'shocking' pause in funding
OL,6,FThe UK Foreign Office said earlier in
OL,7,Fa statement that it was "appalled" by
OL,8,Fallegations against UNRWA staff and
OL,9,Fwould temporarily halt funding while
OL,10,Fan investigation takes place.
OL,12,FThe relief agency has played a key
OL,13,Frole in providing aid for the
OL,14,Fenclave's population amid the
OL,15,Fhumanitarian disaster caused by
OL,16,FIsrael's offensive in the wake of the
OL,17,FOctober 7 attack.
