OL,3,CHead of UNRWA calls on countries to
OL,4,Creconsider 'shocking' pause in funding
OL,6,FMr Lazzarini said it had ordered an
OL,7,Finvestigation after Israel provided
OL,8,Finformation alleging several employees
OL,9,Fplayed a role in Hamas's assault.
OL,11,FThe US state department said claims
OL,12,Fhad been made against 12 employees.
OL,14,FUNRWA has 13,000 staff in Gaza, almost
OL,15,Fall of them Palestinians, ranging from
OL,16,Fteachers in schools that the agency
OL,17,Fruns, to doctors, medical staff and
OL,18,Faid workers.
