OL,3,CHead of UNRWA calls on countries to
OL,4,Creconsider 'shocking' pause in funding
OL,6,FIn its unprecedented October 7 attack,
OL,7,FHamas broke through the security fence
OL,8,Fsurrounding Gaza and stormed nearby
OL,9,FIsraeli communities, killing about
OL,10,F1,200 people and kidnapping some 250.
OL,12,FIsrael's offensive ` one of the
OL,13,Fdeadliest and most destructive in
OL,14,Frecent history ` has killed more than
OL,15,F26,000 Palestinians and left more than
OL,16,F64,400 wounded, according to the
OL,17,Fterritory's Hamas-run health ministry.
